# Component Patterns

## Dialogs

- Use `.dialog-overlay` > `.dialog` > `.dialog-header` + `.dialog-body` + `.dialog-footer` structure
- Dialog tabs: use segmented control pattern (pill container with highlighted active segment), NOT underline tabs
- Active tab: `background: var(--accent); color: var(--text-inverse)`
- Tab buttons must reset: `border-radius: 0` or custom radius, `box-shadow: none`, `border: none`, `outline: none`

## Form Groups

- Use `.form-group` with `label` + `input/select`
- Labels: `font-size: 14px`, `font-weight: 600`, `text-transform: uppercase`, `letter-spacing: 0.06em`, `color: var(--text-secondary)`
- Inputs inside forms: `height: 40px`

## Buttons

- `.btn-primary`: accent bg, inverse text, full-width in dialog forms
- `.btn-secondary`: elevated bg, bordered
- `.btn-ghost`: transparent, text-secondary, 34px height
- `.btn-icon`: square icon button, 28px
- `.btn-danger`: error bg, inverse text

## Context Menus

Account for CSS zoom when positioning:
```tsx
const zoom = parseFloat(document.documentElement.style.zoom) || 1;
setContextMenu({ x: e.clientX / zoom, y: e.clientY / zoom });
```

## Error Banners

Auto-clear after 5 seconds when data is present using `useEffect` with `setTimeout`.
